---
title: Soy and Orange Glazed Pork with Mediterranean Veggies and Couscous
description: We love a bit of fruit on meat action! Everyone loves a bit of apple sauce on their pork, but if you’ve never had orange glazed pork, now’s your chance. We adore the way it works with fluffy couscous and Mediterranean veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-and-orange-glazed-pork-wk3-d2ff4170.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/soy-and-orange-glazed-pork-wk3-f06eb22f.pdf
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 600 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 61 g
  sugar: 8 g
